{"url": "https://people.com/movies/ewan-mcgregors-ex-eve-mavrakis-breaks-her-silence-calls-divorce-disappointing-and-upsetting/", "text": "Ewan McGregor\u2018s ex-wife Eve Mavrakis is breaking her silence about their split after 22 years of marriage.\n\nMavrakis said that while the divorce is \u201cupsetting,\u201d she is moving forward by putting her attention on her family.\n\n\u201cIt\u2019s disappointing and upsetting but my main concern is our four children are okay,\u201d she told The Sun on Sunday.\n\nMcGregor filed for divorce on Jan. 19, citing irreconcilable differences as the reason for their split. The star, 46, has asked for joint custody of their three children: Clara, 21, Jamyan, 16, Esther, 15 and Anouk, 6.\n\nMavrakis\u2019 filed her response, stating that she is asking for sole custody with visitation for her ex, according to the website.\n\nThe documents list the date of separation as May 28th of last year.\n\nBen Gabbe/Getty Images\n\nThe couple announced their split last October, and at the time a family source revealed to PEOPLE that the couple had been separated since last May. The announcement came amid news that McGregor was spotted kissing his Fargo costar Mary Elizabeth Winstead.\n\nChris Pizzello/Invision/AP/REX/Shutterstock\n\nThe Golden Globe winner, 46, took his romance with the actress public in November when he and Winsteadwere photographed walking hand in hand in Los Angeles.\n\nWinstead split from her own husband, Riley Stearns, in May of last year. They were married in 2010.\n\nMcGregor met Mavrakis on the set of the British TV crime series Kavanagh QC and they were married in 1995.", "images": ["https://people.com/thmb/6YMkmjVi3TmowFGegJCAptVBPY4=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Amy-Schumer-Chris-Fischer-111325-68d54c198ba54698b5d309804bf32f3e.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/Bh3W1CuXrVrTbcUrLIErX-fSdE4=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Dwayne-Johnson-and-wife-Dany-Johnson-during-Be-Cool-Los-Angeles-Premiere-110725-3df6d0982ff94ecba1e9aee4cf287f3b.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/tvXMRXdvgA34vBrKl59yNt_BzLc=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/David-Geffen-David-Armstrong-051825-ebea6b6be9714cfc8a10bc99d5fe4f64.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/U1DMPLz94vI8Khnq8LPpi0MiLfQ=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/ewan-mcgregor-family-091224-ff2652c0873d4f329fe4723005ddd86e.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/dgaQEoitjqwo2PUofdvj95PqiM4=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Colin-Firths-Ex-Wife-Livia-Giuggioli-Firth-102725-e7d2dbf3d50f427cac95744fd1630878.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/6BVgFQ30gWgD9XmkUm2j5s90DZk=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/alex-rodriguez-Cynthia-Scurtis-Madonna-111325-33c2de3e05914ed987d94df4aced2d95.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/1eGmrZFjcTwi-wMb8B5c8zavEcI=/343x228/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Amy-Schumer-Chris-Fischer-111325-68d54c198ba54698b5d309804bf32f3e.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/i3yO7KWh5oL6W3qHNuf41NtTgH0=/343x228/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/brittany-cartwright-jax-taylor-042424-2-44111ab94387465fb3c3f9b56068c753.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/Uo8iLTyanrj7eNHYmSXZHwHJbxY=/800x533/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Spencer-Lofranco-112025-56efb2cd379b4817ac0f4d3b10fb37f3.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/bPRr49iSek02jBass9S4e-yomVI=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Drake-and-Serena-Williams-111925-1730587f36384e638ef89c0c54671fc3.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/ZwwCMByuADCsEEW1873K-zFp1S4=/4000x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(999x0:1001x2)/ewan-mcgregor-1-2000-0885ebd9ffb541e5afa1fe65f089d8c5.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/djP0TRoy9vuIloEmCmuanA0N1NY=/800x533/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/quadruple-amputation2-112025-c05ec8d5ca3f44488ab8fd45eb9d724d.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/cPwf16VmAIcMiqmQeutG